summary: An ENB config I\'ve been working on for a while. It\'s my first mod so be gentle and any constructive criticism is appreciated! :D
descriptionHtml:
Only for higher end PCs. This will cost you 20-40FPS. For all of you not familiar with ENB mods, it\'s a high end graphics mod that adds more complex lighting amongst other things. If you want to know more check out the official site!

http://www.enbdev.com/

Installation instructions are included along with the d3d9.dll file required to get the ENB working. :D

If you\'re wanting your game to look exactly like mine here\'s a list of the other graphics enhancing mods I currently have installed.

Pure Waters
IMAGINATOR (Pixar Preset)
Bigger and Boulder
Matso Immersive Rain
Matso Immersive Sun
Customizable Camera
Skyrim Ultra HD Texture Pack
aMidianBorn Roads and Bridges
author: Numinax
